CHANGES
=======

2.8.0
-----

* Release 2.8.0
* Add support for Python 3.13, drop Python 3.8
* api: Add missing \n in error message
* fix missing ']' in warning message
* Actually drop support for Python 3.7
* setup: Use modern variables
* CI: Use modern contexts (pt. 2)

